highlights.text: Bad Bunny has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Me Porto Bonito” is the highest at #4.
“Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 284 weeks straight.
“Layla” by DJ Robin and Schürze is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 75 spots at #120.
“Quevedo: Bzrp Music Sessions, Vol. 52” by Bizarrap and Quevedo is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #3.
